            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EQuietness%20is%20a%20state%20of%20repose%20and%20rest%2C%20of%20no%20longer%20struggling%20and%20fretting.%20God%20wants%20to%20give%20His%20people%20quietness%2C%20and%20quietness%20begins%20with%20righteousness.%20Isaiah%2032%3A17%20says%2C%20%22And%20this%20righteousness%20will%20bring%20peace.%20Quietness%20and%20confidence%20will%20fill%20the%20land%20forever.%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhen%20we%20are%20sure%20that%20our%20sins%20are%20forgiven%20and%20we%20are%20in%20right%20standing%20with%20God%2C%20a%20deep%20quietness%20fills%20our%20hearts.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EFrom%20that%20quietness%20arises%20confidence.%20We%20base%20our%20confidence%20on%20our%20righteousness%2C%20knowing%20that%20we%20are%20welcome%20to%20ask%20Him%20for%20anything%20we%20need.%20We%20must%20be%20confident%20that%20%22He%20will%20respond%20instantly%20to%20the%20sound%20of%20%5Bour%5D%20cries%22%20(Isaiah%2030%3A19).%20John%20said%2C%20%22We%20can%20be%20confident%20that%20he%20will%20listen%20to%20us%20whenever%20we%20ask%20him%20for%20anything%20in%20line%20with%20his%20will.%20And%20if%20we%20know%20he%20is%20listening%20when%20we%20make%20our%20requests%2C%20we%20can%20be%20sure%20that%20he%20will%20give%20us%20what%20we%20ask%20for%22%20(1%20John%205%3A14-15).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ERighteousness%2C%20quietness%2C%20and%20then%20confidence%20will%20bring%20us%20through%20affliction%2C%20for%20Jesus%20is%20like%20a%20%22cool%20shadow%20of%20a%20large%20rock%20in%20a%20hot%20and%20weary%20land%22%20(Isaiah%2032%3A2).%20Let's%20stay%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20His%20presence!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
