            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Isaiah.30:12-33:9",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EIsaiah%2030%3A12-33%3A9%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_30_12%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-fl-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20reply%20of%20the%20Holy%20One%20of%20Israel%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BBecause%20you%20despise%20what%20I%20tell%20you%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20trust%20instead%20in%20oppression%20and%20lies%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_30_13%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3Ecalamity%20will%20come%20upon%20you%20suddenly%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Elike%20a%20bulging%20wall%20that%20bursts%20and%20falls.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EIn%20an%20instant%20it%20will%20collapse%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20come%20crashing%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_30_14%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20will%20be%20smashed%20like%20a%20piece%20of%20pottery%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eshattered%20so%20completely%20that%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ethere%20won%26%23x2019%3Bt%20be%20a%20piece%20big%20enough%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eto%20carry%20coals%20from%20a%20fireplace%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eor%20a%20little%20water%20from%20the%20well.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_30_15%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethe%20Holy%20One%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BOnly%20in%20returning%20to%20me%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20resting%20in%20me%20will%20you%20be%20saved.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EIn%20quietness%20and%20confidence%20is%20your%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EBut%20you%20would%20have%20none%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_30_16%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20said%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BNo%2C%20we%20will%20get%20our%20help%20from%20Egypt.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThey%20will%20give%20us%20swift%20horses%20for%20riding%20into%20battle.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EBut%20the%20only%20swiftness%20you%20are%20going%20to%20see%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eis%20the%20swiftness%20of%20your%20enemies%20chasing%20you!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_30_17%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20of%20them%20will%20chase%20a%20thousand%20of%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EFive%20of%20them%20will%20make%20all%20of%20you%20flee.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EYou%20will%20be%20left%20like%20a%20lonely%20flagpole%20on%20a%20hill%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eor%20a%20tattered%20banner%20on%20a%20distant%20mountaintop.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_30_18%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EBlessings%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20People%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20must%20wait%20for%20you%20to%20come%20to%20him%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eso%20he%20can%20show%20you%20his%20love%20and%20compassion.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EFor%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20a%20faithful%20God.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EBlessed%20are%20those%20who%20wait%20for%20his%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_30_19%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EO%26%23xA0%3Bpeople%20of%20Zion%2C%20who%20live%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eyou%20will%20weep%20no%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EHe%20will%20be%20gracious%20if%20you%20ask%20for%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EHe%20will%20surely%20respond%20to%20the%20sound%20of%20your%20cries.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_30_20%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EThough%20the%20Lord%20gave%20you%20adversity%20for%20food%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20suffering%20for%20drink%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ehe%20will%20still%20be%20with%20you%20to%20teach%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EYou%20will%20see%20your%20teacher%20with%20your%20own%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_30_21%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%2230%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EYour%20own%20ears%20will%20hear%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ERight%20behind%20you%20a%20voice%20will%20say%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BT